運輸業風險與危機管理RISK AND CRISIS MANAGEMENT FOR TRANSPORTATION INDUSTRY






開課系所 Department/Institute:  交管所          Transportation and Communication Management Science
開課教師 Instructor:   黃國平 Hwang, Kevin-P                
開課學年 Academic Year:   0103
